Usage: setHierMode [-help] [-reset] [-addAntennaCell {true|false}]
                   [-optStage {preCTS|postCTS|unset}]

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-reset                                    # Resets all or specified options to default value
-addAntennaCell {true|false}              # add antenna diode to interface load
                                          # (bool, default=false)
-optStage {preCTS|postCTS|unset}          # Turn on default settings for
                                          # hierarchical flows at different
                                          # optimization stage.
                                          # (enums={preCTS postCTS unset}, default=unset)